WEBVTT

00:00:01.520 --> 00:00:17.070
Jesus, tired out as he was from the journey, was sitting at the well.

00:00:17.070 --> 00:00:22.460
It was about the sixth hour.

00:00:22.460 --> 00:00:34.859
A woman of Samaria came to draw water.

00:00:34.859 --> 00:00:35.859
Give me a drink.

00:00:35.859 --> 00:00:46.439
How is it that you, despite being a Jew, ask me for a drink, even though I'm a Samaritan

00:00:46.439 --> 00:00:48.850
woman?

00:00:48.850 --> 00:00:54.170
For Jews have no dealings with Samaritans.

00:00:54.170 --> 00:01:01.170
A woman of Samaritans, tired out as he was from the journey, was sitting at the well.
